txt.en: You have slaughtered many hendrevail in eastern Osgiliath.
'These hendrevail keep diving at my troops! These pesky birds are causing a lot of frustration!\n\n'Take care of them. I don't care how, just get rid of them! Still don't get it? Kill those birds!'
Dulglok commands you to kill those pesky hendrevail that keep diving at Orcs.
You have slaughtered many hendrevail and now the Orcs won't keep thinking they're getting attacked by filthy Men archers.
Hendrevail can be found on the eastern side of Osgiliath.\n\nYou should defeat the pesky hendrevail.
